title: Lives of Others - PSP Video
description:
The Lives of Others

Is a German movie in the days before the fall of the Berlin Wall (1984) when the Stasi had full control of the lives of all the citizens in the DDR.

I found it an excellent movie, highly recommended.

This is in PSP video format - use PSP Video Manager (shareware) to upload to the PSP (or just connect the PSP via USB and copy the two files in \\MP_ROOT\\101ANV01 (I have a suspicion the latter is just a random name, but don\&#039;t know enough to be positive)

This was created with Xilisoft\&#039;s PSP video Converter - an excellent piece of software (I actually paid for it - I only approve of pirating Micro$oft shit ;-)
